message.entry: FFT Size should be positive and an integer power of 2.
Number of spectrum averages should be a positive integer.
The normalized loop bandwidth of fine frequency compensation PLL should be a positive real number.
The damping factor of fine frequency compensation PLL should be a positive real number.
The normalized loop bandwidth of timing recovery PLL should be a positive real number.
The damping factor of timing recovery PLL should be a positive real number.
The loop gain should be a positive real number.
The maximum gain should be a positive real number.
The threshold should be a positive real number.
